_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":31773,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/malik-sunnah-is-ark-of-nuh\/","url_meta":{"origin":27956,"position":0},"title":"Malik on Salvation: The Sunnah is like the Ark of Noah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn \u2018Asakir reported: Malik ibn Anas, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cThe Sunnah is like the Ark of Noah. Whoever boards it will be saved, and whoever does not board it will drown.\u201d Source: Ta\u0304ri\u0304kh Dimashq 12275 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0639\u0633\u0627\u0643\u0631 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643 \u0628\u0646 \u0623\u0646\u0633 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0651\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0633\u064e\u0641\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e\u0629\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19468,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/09\/malik-sunnah-my-opinion\/","url_meta":{"origin":27956,"position":1},"title":"Malik on Sunnah: If my opinion contradicts Sunnah, leave it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 9, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abdul Barr reported: Malik ibn Anas, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI am only a human being. I make mistakes and I am correct, so investigate my opinions. Whatever agrees with the Book and the Sunnah, take it. Whatever does not agree with them, abandon it.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25806,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/27\/malik-asma-wa-sifat-kayfiyyah\/","url_meta":{"origin":27956,"position":2},"title":"Malik on Divinity: Attributes of Allah affirmed, modality unknown","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 27, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Nafi\u2019 reported: Imam Malik, may Allah have mercy on him, was asked about the saying of Allah Almighty, \"The Most Merciful rose above the Throne,\" (20:5). The man said, \u201cHow is His rising?\u201d Malik said, \u201cThe rising is acknowledged, its modality is unknown, and asking about it is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25304,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/22\/ahmad-follow-sunnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":27956,"position":3},"title":"Ahmad on Sunnah: Do not blindly follow me, follow Hadith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abdul Barr reported: Imam Ahmad ibn Hanbal, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cAl-Awza\u2019i had opinions, Malik had opinions, Sufyan al-Thawri had opinions. Each of them had opinions, and it is all the same to me. Indeed, the proof is only in the narrations.\u201d In another narration, Imam\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12186,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/14\/ibn-wahb-fiqh-malik-layth\/","url_meta":{"origin":27956,"position":4},"title":"Ibn Wahb on Fiqh: I would be led astray, if not for Imam Malik","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 14, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Dhahabi reported: Ibn Wahb, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWere it not for Malik and Al-Layth, I would have been ruined. I used to believe that everything narrated about the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, should be acted upon.\u201d Source:\u00a0Siyar A\u02bbla\u0304m al-Nubala\u0304\u02bc 8\/148 Ibn Abi Layla\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10438,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/12\/19\/left-you-with-kitab-sunnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":27956,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: I have left you with the Book, the Sunnah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI have left you with two matters which will never lead you astray, as long as you hold to them: the Book of Allah and the Sunnah of his Prophet.\u201d Source: al-Muwat\u0323t\u0323a' 1661 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to\u00a0Ibn\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuamin